## 四、数据库字段对照

### `fb_ads`

`ad_id`, `ad_name`, `spend`, `budget`, `cpm`, `post_id`, `story_id`, `date_start`, `date_end`

### `account_shop_mapping`

`account_id`, `account_name`, `shop_id`, `shop_domain`, `shop_name`

### `shoplazza_utm`

| 库字段 | Shoplazza API | 用途 |
|--------|--------------|------|
| `uv` | `view_client_count` | 单次连接点击花费分母 |
| `add_to_cart` | `add_to_cart_count` | 单次加购费用分母 |
| `begin_checkout` | `begin_checkout_count` | 单次结账费用分母 |
| `orders` | `orders_count` | 单次成效花费分母 |
| `sales` | `product_sales` | ROAS 分子 |

